---
// Work Overview Section - The Complete System
---

<section class="section-padding-xl bg-white">
  <div class="container-premium">
    
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <span class="text-xs font-display tracking-widest text-secondary uppercase mb-4">The Complete System</span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary leading-tight mb-8">
        Four Parts. One System.<br>Complete Results.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-secondary max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        The work is never sold as separate pieces because they only work together as a complete infrastructure.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- System Visualization -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-32">
      <!-- Central Hub -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Center Circle -->
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-20">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center">
            <div class="px-4">
              <div class="text-xs font-display tracking-widest uppercase mb-1">Complete</div>
              <div class="text-sm font-bold">System</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Connection Lines -->
        <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full" style="z-index: 10;">
          <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="25%" y2="25%" stroke="#e5e5e5" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="75%" y2="25%" stroke="#e5e5e5" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="25%" y2="75%" stroke="#e5e5e5" stroke-width="2"/>
          <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="75%" y2="75%" stroke="#e5e5e5" stroke-width="2"/>
        </svg>
        
        <!-- Four Parts Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-16 relative" style="z-index: 15;">
          <!-- Part 1: Technical Foundation -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="card-premium hover:shadow-premium-lg transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="mb-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-display text-accent tracking-widest uppercase">Part 01</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-primary mb-4">Technical Foundation</h3>
              <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Fast, clean Astro website that passes every Google technical check. Speed, mobile, security, accessibility, structured markup, AI crawler access.
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-secondary">Google Technical Checks</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-secondary">Mobile Compatibility</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-secondary">Security & Accessibility</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Part 2: Single Source of Truth -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="card-premium hover:shadow-premium-lg transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="mb-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-display text-accent tracking-widest uppercase">Part 02</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-primary mb-4">Single Source of Truth</h3>
              <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Sanity CMS as the central nervous system. Every piece of business information stored once, published everywhere simultaneously.
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-secondary">One Place to Update</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-secondary">Instant Sync</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-secondary">No Developer Needed</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Part 3: Google & AI Presence -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="card-premium hover:shadow-premium-lg transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="mb-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-display text-accent tracking-widest uppercase">Part 03</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-primary mb-4">Google & AI Presence</h3>
              <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Schema markup from Sanity data makes Google read your business as structured information. Rich results, Maps visibility, AI inclusion.
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-secondary">Rich Search Results</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-secondary">Google Maps Ready</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-secondary">AI Search Compatible</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Part 4: Lead Management -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="card-premium hover:shadow-premium-lg transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="mb-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-display text-accent tracking-widest uppercase">Part 04</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-primary mb-4">Lead Management</h3>
              <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Simple lead capture and tracking built into the same Sanity dashboard. Manage enquiries from the same place you manage your business info.
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-secondary">Structured Leads</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-secondary">Status Tracking</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                  <span class="text-secondary">No Separate CRM</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- System Benefits -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-primary mb-4">Why It Only Works as a Complete System</h3>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-primary mb-2">Technical Foundation Enables Everything Else</h4>
            <p class="text-secondary">
              Without a technically sound base, structured data won't be read correctly, CMS updates won't propagate properly, and lead capture will fail at critical moments.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-primary mb-2">Single Source Powers Structured Data</h4>
            <p class="text-secondary">
              Schema markup only works when it's fed from a consistent, reliable data source. Manual updates create inconsistencies that break Google's trust.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-primary mb-2">Structured Data Drives Discoverability</h4>
            <p class="text-secondary">
              Google's rich results and AI search inclusion depend entirely on properly structured, consistent business information fed from your central system.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-primary mb-2">Lead Management Completes the Loop</h4>
            <p class="text-secondary">
              All the discoverability in the world is useless without a system to capture and manage the enquiries it generates. It must be integrated, not added later.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-block p-8 bg-primary text-white rounded-2xl">
          <p class="text-xl font-display font-bold mb-4">The Result</p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            A business that is permanently discoverable, permanently credible, and permanently in control of its digital presence—without ongoing dependency on anyone else.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>
